import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { LoginService } from '../../services/login.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-page5', templateUrl: './page5.component.html', styleUrls: ['./page5.component.css'] }) export class Page5Component implements OnInit { buttonStats: any[] = []; constructor(private loginService: LoginService) { } ngOnInit(): void { const userId = '1'; // Kullanıcı ID'sini buraya koyun (örneğin: login olan kullanıcının ID'si) this.loginService.getButtonStats(userId).subscribe(data => { this.buttonStats = data.buttonStats; }, error => { console.error('Error fetching button stats', error); }); } }
